{"tid":250804,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"花千萬送禮賀奪標,大衛雷斯豪得起","createTime":"2017-05-20T11:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T18:18:33.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa664dccea9f04bfaa4c53ad84586494eafe1839","tid":250804,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"車路士重奪英超錦標，梗係要賀賀佢，其中後衞大衛雷斯仲豪花咗超過100萬鎊（約1,000萬港元）買禮物畀隊友、領隊干地、班主阿巴莫域治同埋自己，紀念今次勝利，總之就大家happy。<br />\n<br />\n雷斯今次買喺禮物既高科又名貴，係Senturion智能車匙，外形似手鐲，由貴金钃同埋碳纖造，但其實係智能車匙，適用於賓利、法利拉及Bugatti等名車。據講，為咗突顯班主阿巴嘅尊貴身份，佢嘅智能車匙仲係用有50億年歷史嘅隕石造添呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2a3b552b308203a58e2253d68c16b92a1b7178","tid":250804,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2354b8dca379b234045a174d7ce2bb1373e77b1c","tid":250804,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"兩個月人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cbfd78681a4722e083db84e0ae1888e00da124","tid":250804,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:28:02.000Z","msg":"數百萬當係碎銀...super!"},{"pid":"f652ea9b5baf29f084c5b5598b6f98bd8d12f429","tid":250804,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩個月人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對佢地黎講真係兩個月人工，成千萬港紙真係買到樓，點解D球員可以咁有錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab43d189b8e1b8805eb55f1f2423071a9cc97904","tid":250804,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"金錢足球可恥"},{"pid":"de5733bc409854269b33815d0c6e4d1395